msgstr "Al-Thurayyan seuraaja"

#. TRANSLATORS: Al-Mijdah is a proper name meaning the star of rain or the
#. fork referring to the shape of the Hyades
msgid "Al-Mijdah"
msgstr "Al-Mijdah"

msgid "The follower"
msgstr "Seuraaja"

msgid "The special camel"
msgstr "Erityinen kameli"

msgid "The star on the head of the advance twin"
